@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_invjpm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v0
    v0 = wp.abs(v1)
    v1 = (wp.sin(tmp) * (wp.exp(v2 + 0.08) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.88)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs((tmp + 0.35 / v0 + 0.08)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(v1) + v2)
    data[tid] = v0
